title: Sunset Yoga Series
description: Join us on the lawn for a 60-minute sunset flow with Sweat Yoga, held the first Tuesday of each month from 6–7 PM. Unwind under the open sky as we guide you through an all-levels yoga session designed to reset your mind and body. Bring your mat, your friends, and enjoy the summer evening vibes with us.

title: Summer Night Market
description: Introducing Playa Vista Nights! Join us every Wednesday, for a boutique farmers' market with delicious eats, local makers and laid back summer vibes. Brought to you by Farmhabitpv !

title: Playa Vista Farmer’s Market
description: Saturdays | 9am - 2pm Located in vibrant Runway, Playa Vista, this takes place each Saturday, rain or shine, from 9-2pm. Market goers will find organic fruits, seasonal vegetables, local meat, fresh flowers, baked bread , french pastries , artisanal goat, cow and cashew cheese , nut-butter , salsa and guacamole, Peruvian Arepas, wood-fired pizza, handmade jewelry, and lots more! The Market hosts live music and a KidZone with interactive performances and crafts. Ample parking available in the Runway Mall parking garage. #farmermarkpv

title: RUNWAY Kids Club
description: Join us this summer for Kids Club: Family Yoga with Zooga, happening every 2nd Wednesday of the month, June through August, from 10:00–11:00 AM! Stretch, move, and play together in a fun-filled family yoga class designed for parents and little ones. Led by Zooga’s expert instructors, this session blends movement, music, and connection, followed by a special music session from Brella. Come ready to play, laugh, and make summer memories!

title: Creative Communal | August
description: Get ready for another exciting Creative Communal event! It’s the perfect opportunity to stop by and shop a diverse selection of amazing local artisan makers and vendors to find the perfect gift! GRAB THE WHOLE FAM (PUPS INCLUDED) AND JOIN US FOR AN AMAZING EXPERIENCE! 30+ Local vendors and artisans Photo Opportunity Live Music PLENTY OF FUN FOR EVERYONE - PET FRIENDLY + KID FRIENDLY + LOCAL MAKERS + JEWELRY MAKERS + LEATHER GOODS + BOUTIQUES + KIDS BOUTIQUE + MEN’S APPAREL + DOG GOODS + FINE ART + HOME GOODS + GOOD GRUB + LIVE MUSIC + PHOTO OP + FREE ADMISSION✨ 40 LOCAL MAKERS

title: Movie Under the Stars
description: Join us for an evening of entertainment at RUNWAY, with our new Summer Series, " Movie Under the Stars "! Movie Under the Stars – Bring a blanket or lawn chair – Swing by early for snacks or a drink – Settle in and let the summer vibes roll Catch cult classics, family favorites, and surprise hits all summer long. Free admission. Registration and good company required. Schedule: 6/27: Moana 2 7/15: Bridesmaids 8/18: The Parent Trap

title: RUNWAY x The Fleuria: Silent Reading Parties
description: Bring your current read or explore The Fleuria’s swoon-worthy collection of romance titles. Don’t forget to join the book swap, trade an old favorite for your next obsession. Pack your own picnic or grab the perfect snack from your favorite spot before settling in. After the reading winds down, swing by Joliet for a cocktail and keep the good vibes going.
